title: The Winner (David Baldacci)
description: This is not my torrent originally. I tried to find the place I got it from to give the person credit, but I don't remember where I found it. So, it you are the original uploader, thanks. I have been looking for this audio book for years in mp3 format and unabridged. It is done at a low bitrate, but the sound is pretty good, especially for being ripped off cassette tapes. I am so happy to find this finally, and again, thanks to the original uploader. I made it into one big mp3 file because that is how I like my audio books, you can split it up if you want.
